{"tid":1626334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日到我地打返一手好牌！！！","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:44:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:54:27.000Z","uid":73722,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"490f4949f282bd72b7775e6bf7898be0a95666a1","tid":1626334,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"係呢度容許我先同所有手足講聲多謝，只要係呢場出過力既都係同路人<br />\n<br />\n今日上水既夢比政府知蒙面法嚇唔到裝修師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角到尖沙咀既人鍊比政府知你一樣鎮壓唔到和平示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有就係最近既裝修行動其實我地都分化緊對面！只係為錢既商家佬遲早同政府割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和平遊行政府唔理，我地克服到<br />\n黑社會打人，我地克服到<br />\n政府強權打壓，我地一樣克服到<br />\n<br />\n721唔見人831打死人101槍殺人<br />\n<br />\n最後一句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三百萬香港人，我地聽日港島見</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">想發夢既等夜晚返自己屋企附近</span>"},{"pid":"212e8ad5c9fa1d4b567ee16c8a0e6d6fbe5f8ca5","tid":1626334,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」都用緊急法立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=YADvn44w83N9IBOkVydrkzMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=fcf621ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"ca6fde2ecbeb0f16cf848d12e06258073afc0cd5","tid":1626334,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"212e8ad5c9fa1d4b567ee16c8a0e6d6fbe5f8ca5","tid":1626334,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep